Apache SOLR Multisite Filter

This Drupal 7 module restricts the search results from a shared Apache SOLR index to the current site only.


[REQUIREMENTS]

- apachesolr



[INSTALL]

1. Clone the module into your DRUPAL_ROOT/sites/all/modules/
2. Navigate to DRUPAL_URL/admin/modules and enable the module.
3. Navigate to DRUPAL_URL/admin/config/search/apachesolr/multisite and enable the filter.


